      "content": "10k seems kinda low though if i really want to feel the effects quickly. i read online that some people do way higher than that to completely saturate their system. if i tell my doctor i want to do 50k for just two weeks to front-load it, is there actually any real medical reason they'd say no? it's only for a short time so it shouldn't be a big deal right?",
